    "description": " <br><br><strong>Choose your class</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109170/extras/e6ebc79a94e011b66d3c14e72c2c4053.poster.avif?t=1760115659\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109170/extras/e6ebc79a94e011b66d3c14e72c2c4053.webm?t=1760115659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109170/extras/e6ebc79a94e011b66d3c14e72c2c4053.mp4?t=1760115659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Naked with a stick? Armor to protect you? Daggers with poison?<br>Choose how you want to face your phobias and destroy them all!!<br>Each class has different stats and unique abilities!<br><br><strong>Explore and collect</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109170/extras/97865fbd0ae3e2784ee81466d104de65.poster.avif?t=1760115659\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109170/extras/97865fbd0ae3e2784ee81466d104de65.webm?t=1760115659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109170/extras/97865fbd0ae3e2784ee81466d104de65.mp4?t=1760115659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Enter into your mind and navigate through the vast network of neurons.<br>Get items that will improve your character to free them from your phobias and get rewards for it.<br>Discover secrets, hidden places and make friends along the way!<br><br><strong>Meet friends</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109170/extras/c4e9d4435e244934650fa2403a9efc95.poster.avif?t=1760115659\" width=368 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109170/extras/c4e9d4435e244934650fa2403a9efc95.webm?t=1760115659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109170/extras/c4e9d4435e244934650fa2403a9efc95.mp4?t=1760115659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Everyone knows that adventures are always more bearable if you are accompanied by people willing to help you.<br>You will find the best professionals that will make your way easier.<br>I won’t lie to you though. If you want to get help there is always a price you will have to pay.<br><br><strong>Fight your phobias</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109170/extras/2712d92805f7462b11a54df11576c379.poster.avif?t=1760115659\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109170/extras/2712d92805f7462b11a54df11576c379.webm?t=1760115659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109170/extras/2712d92805f7462b11a54df11576c379.mp4?t=1760115659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Free your mind from your worst phobias!<br>Fight against them in a frantic turn-based combat!<br>Now you attack! Now they attack! You again! Them again! Unbelievable!<br>Dodge all the attacks they throw at you with your great moving skills!<br>Move from side to side, jump, dash, cling to the wall, do whatever it takes to avoid being hit!<br><br><strong>Status Effects</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109170/extras/c559488d95103e94dfd7c5dd96cc6623.poster.avif?t=1760115659\" width=560 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109170/extras/c559488d95103e94dfd7c5dd96cc6623.webm?t=1760115659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109170/extras/c559488d95103e94dfd7c5dd96cc6623.mp4?t=1760115659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Poison, Burn, Freezing, Wet, Electrify and Bleeding.<br>Be careful not to be affected by any of them.<br>On the contrary! Apply all these states to your phobias and make your battle end much sooner.<br>Actually, you won’t be able to apply all of them.<br>Some have synergies, while others negate each other.",
